It's never comfortable anytime I have to articulate my carpel tunnel wrists
around the back of the fan shroud. For myself, I prefer to use a 10" swivel
extension on a bolt from underneath the car and keep the nut insert or
install one if it isn't there. It is easier for me and I have enough trouble
with the starter motor bolt/nut. Do you have pics?

